  </head>
  <body>
    <a href="index.html">Back to Home</a>
    <p> The United Arab Emirates Is a eastren Part of the Arabian Peninsula located on the southeastern coast of the Persian Gulf and the northwestern coast of the Gulf of Oman. The UAE consists of seven emirates and was founded on 2 December 1971 as a federation, after UK armed forces left the region. The States Are:
      <ul>
        <li> Abu Dhabi</li>
        <li> Dubai </li>
        <li> Sharjah </li>
        <li> Ajman </li>
        <li> Umm AI Quwian </li>
        <li> Fujairh </li>
        </ul>
    <p> Artifacts uncovered in the UAE show a history of human habitation, transmigration and trade spanning over 125,000 years.[3] The area was previously home to the Magan people known to the Sumerians, who traded with both coastal towns and bronze miners and smelters from the interior. A rich history of trade with the Harappan culture of the Indus Valley is also evidenced by finds of jewelry and other items and there is also extensive early evidence of trade with Afghanistan </p>
